### mousemove 事件
- canvas.addEventListener('mousemove', (e) => { ... })
- 计算：const rect = canvas.getBoundingClientRect(); const x = e.clientX - rect.left; const y = e.clientY - rect.top
- 网格坐标：col = Math.floor(x / TILE_SIZE); row = Math.floor(y / TILE_SIZE)
- 如果有存活单位（manager.getUnitAt(row, col)?.isAlive()）：
  ```
  const u = manager.getUnitAt(row, col)!;
